text: Money in the Bank (2016) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view and livestreaming show made by WWE. It took place on June 19, 2016 at the T-Mobile Arena in Paradise, Nevada. It was the seventh Money in the Bank event held by WWE. ==Matches== == References == == Other websites == * Category:WWE Money in the Bank Category:Nevada Category:2016 in sports
